Usage: objdiff.exe [-C <chdir>] [-L <log-level>] [-V] [--no-color] <command>
                   [<args>]

A local diffing tool for decompilation projects.

Options:
  -C, --chdir <chdir>          Change working directory.
  -L, --log-level <log_level>  Minimum logging level. (Default: info) Possible
                               values: error, warn, info, debug, trace
  -V, --version                Print version information and exit.
      --no-color               Disable color output. (env: NO_COLOR)
  -h, --help                   Show this help message and exit.

Commands:
  diff                         Diff two object files. (Interactive or one-shot
                               mode)
  report                       Generate a progress report for a project.

